{"tid":848914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴68M荃灣線有靚女司機","createTime":"2018-10-05T09:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T11:01:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3041d5d7196bb67fb7a5527c4cf5ca0a3f39ce","tid":848914,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Af9WPWmFqaEZW_i2YVuCoA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQ0O2g9NTky/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/heawork.tumblr.com/ced7f85e23d3da4ab6e2403f2a7c85ea\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAf9WPWmFqaEZW_i2YVuCoA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQ0O2g9NTky%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fheawork.tumblr.com%2Fced7f85e23d3da4ab6e2403f2a7c85ea&h=2be7375d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前傳媒大肆報道城巴靚女司機，對九巴相當唔公平。其實呢個世界，行行出美女，尤其在男多女少的工種，只要樣貌正正常常唔太差，都可以登上「女神」寶座。<br />\n<br />\n今次主角終於落在以下呢位九巴女司機身上，有網民在社交平台張貼疑似九巴美女司機的自拍照，有晒角度兼落重effect，就算真人版可能打個7折，但都above average。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n4rnRBm1IOpScGvLd_W2cg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/heawork.tumblr.com/212867f2a70bb786e7dcfc52611d1610\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fn4rnRBm1IOpScGvLd_W2cg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fheawork.tumblr.com%2F212867f2a70bb786e7dcfc52611d1610&h=810ed3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有眼利網民似乎認得呢位美女司機，立即報料話係來往元朗西及荃灣的 68M 巴士，搞到一眾巴打都想搭上呢架68M，遇見「女神」。唔知今次又會唔會引來一股朝聖熱潮呢?"},{"pid":"4729b0ec6d948cae6f6328808893d202375030e9","tid":848914,"uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"又黎女人返工系列"},{"pid":"4abc37266ce691fda9c5249b5ccda4244b95e933","tid":848914,"uid":48334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"ci